description:
*Gay Wedding In Arthur* | When many of us were children, we grew up on PBS Kids shows like _Dragon Tales, Reading Rainbow, and Clifford The Big Red Dog._ We fell in love with the characters in these shows and all their quirky personalities that made us laugh. Over time, we built a trust and may even trust these same shows with our children now. But times are changing. Are you aware of what your kids are watching and what they are being taught? @PBS @PBSKIDS
